dc_title_s: Double indexed street map of Chicago
dc_description_s: Shows streets, boulevards, car lines, rail roads, elevated railways, car lines and elevated railways on same street and motor coach routes.; Includes indexes to streets and addresses and inset map of the Chicago business district.; "The right map for every purpose."; "Courtesy, service, workmanship."|94 x 54 centimeters|Scale approximately 1:48,000|City Maps
